Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？ 有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來你想讀哪本？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這段時間漂了不少推理系的完本過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真喜歡書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 其實我有件想做來試試的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別笑我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實啦 我想像推理小說裡的主角一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的與怪人對決 然後解決事件試試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後再以這為藍本寫出小說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清正先生肯定寫得出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必寫出來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 不過我沒多少文采啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:25.37,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)}充滿謎團 偵探（後篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾名——紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難...難道真有真人存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那招待狀果然是你發出來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼綾音看到的「我」也...？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百面怪人 說的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底有什麼企圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:03:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美麗少女的慘叫和佈滿恐懼的臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而為此我做的第一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是把島上最癢的東森薯蕷汁灑到了那位少女的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管其不治自癒 但會一直癢到下個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而能盡快治好她的 就只有我手上的解毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 還不快點交過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然將我重要的客人...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑夜小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我視你為敵人 予以消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑夜小姐 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要解毒藥 就在月圓之期內抓到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 逃得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計笑夜小姐又把什麼當成敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是餘興節目？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑夜為我們著想 特意放煙火給我們看？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊泡著溫泉一邊看煙火 真是風雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要亂來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉也是人 會死的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...好像被逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能躲過我的攻擊 雖是敵人值得敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 我們先回月見亭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想這還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要泡多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得大家來一趟聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天的時間這麼快就要過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:05:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真 真正的樂趣現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 接下來只剩睡覺了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴真是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上能做的可不止睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 此話不假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切磋劍藝一整晚也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的不是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個 是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼玲玲說是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...呀...這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人殿下帶進屋 扔進被褥裡侍寑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著鬧上一整晚...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 說的是寑技的特訓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小忍 我估計你又想錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來大姐頭 這次可不准偷跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是...想...想...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃我也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們現在聊的不是大庭廣眾下能說的話題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 行人跟我是一個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起睡的當然是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼話嘛 阿鈴都一起睡了那麼久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 今晚就讓給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 沒嫁入門之前怎麼能...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說大家可還沒成年哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去沒個完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡輪到我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又跑來出壞點子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定沒好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你想用什麼方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家在行人回來之前回到各自的寢室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後寫信給行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫什麼信？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫「若想與我共度良宵 就請到我寢室來」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 讓行人自己來選啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 挑戰書哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 根本方向就不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可行人也許會誰都不選去空屋子睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們讓那路人馬在空屋子待機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若行人過去了就把他趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人到底最喜歡誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚一切都將大白於天下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人最喜歡誰...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼肯定是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥啦 肯定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 也可能是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 肯定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從他的行動模式來看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會變裝 混進同伴之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耐心等待出手的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼請包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真是假 我肯定能認出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 不愧是科技的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼特殊能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊 我只是一一拉她們的臉來確認罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給笑夜小姐你來拉 連真人的臉都會掉下來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑夜小姐你怎麼能反過來傷害客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這種原始方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼更科學的手段嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如用紅外線透視
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如用聲紋或者太陽進行個體識別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪可能有那麼方便的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是SF
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 笑夜你的存在本身就已經是SF了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 這裡只好不依靠科學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以王道來推動劇情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王道？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 也就是對偵探來說最大的武器 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 是頭腦 也就是推理能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著我 紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次比試我接下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人殿下...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會來 不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會來 不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會來 不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的不算 練習罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來才是正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只是睡覺 也不能讓旦那看到我不體面的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要稍微打扮一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人怎麼還不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了和他玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人...已經看過信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡的女孩子...會去誰的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這用的難道是宮本武藏打敗佐佐木小次郎時的戰法？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先擾亂我心神 趁機再一口氣決勝負...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會中計的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小忍？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千影？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到慘叫過來一看...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小忍 你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師...師父...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來她受到了強烈的抓癢按摩 動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要按摩到這程度...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎剛才有人在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人肉按摩椅？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是紅夜叉 千影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他出現了 真正的紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 那個招待狀果然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 而且剛才綾音犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小忍就是第二犧牲者咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去 還會有第三第四犧牲者...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再讓你為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這...這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 若變成和行人共度漫漫長夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定...會變成這樣...變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音 你不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的背癢得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手...手又碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這一帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 更下面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是...哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音的皮膚真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有啦 行人殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太癢了好像又進入妄想世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣應該能輕鬆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉那傢伙...接下來又想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在下個犧牲者出現之前 想想對策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是梅梅的慘叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅？沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:12:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像臉上被灑了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白白的...難道又是薯蕷汁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？身上癢不癢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 你怎麼了 梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你選了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼...小女子不才...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 不是平常那個害羞的梅梅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我灑在那女孩身上的並不是薯蕷汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灑在那女孩身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一沾上就會瞬間變得H起來的 蘑菇汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然解毒藥在這兒...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過少年你好像挺爽的 不要也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩位 梅梅拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼快就走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣睡著了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵醒她又有點過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個笑笑藥就算了吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次休想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得不錯 保持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要這樣才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事啊 從剛才就這麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣怎麼睡啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尿床？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃得就是快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 不來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 不來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡不用擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 是玲玲的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲玲 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼在這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐你真見外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旦那 你選了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份御姐狂氣 百分百是真正的小尊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 既然如此只好一個一個查了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 幹嘛 為何話都不給說就被趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個追丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑夜小姐攻要害讓她睡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才上面有個可疑黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 是二樓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特大紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:15:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你不是看了信來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是很明白 不過鈴你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等下 行人 你在說什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我讓你看證明 把眼睛閉上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人？ 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是假貨 就是我剛才提到的紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴應該看得出吧？我們每天都生活在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...這邊的行人 又感覺跟平常有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊 仔細看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適可而止 給我離鈴遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺...殺氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這種時候一般不是享受真假對比的樂趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那邊是真身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰管你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我有點得意忘形了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你無路可逃了 紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然在小說中你最後也沒有暴露身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就由我在這兒揭開你的真面目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒發現你是被我引來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年 你有恐高症吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丟臉 嚇得動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前追我的那男人可比你有趣多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你模仿他是絕對做不到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不准說絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 解毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉掉掉掉...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如傳聞般是個有趣的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得那孩子會看上他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我久違的創作欲湧上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼下個月圓之夜再會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點洞察力就想揭開我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差得遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他很好強的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次相遇的時候 最好小心一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時是以忍者般身手引發事件的紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時又是以那事件為藍本寫小說的謎之匿名作家 靜丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 他的真身...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是我家媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小千 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切順利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實如小千所說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個很適合做第二代主人公的有趣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪人的宿敵就是要好強的才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能讀到靜丸的新作了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的粉絲肯定會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 畢竟是我約好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等有時間 再寫本新作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與那位靜丸一號粉絲作的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得你演繹紅夜叉 以及寫小說的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了吸引那個喜歡推理小說的男人注意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啦 我會害羞的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果到最後 還是沒明白行人會選誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你臉上除了一絲遺憾 還有一絲放心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 我們的惡夢之夜結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 紅夜叉的犧牲者實在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:24.10,*Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,沒中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉 這份禮我總有一天會還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總有一天會揭開你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我記著～～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:56.68,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)}{\pos(447.407,600)}{\1c&H8c3b30&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}被假扮 彭彭彭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到以自己為原型的小說 心情真複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且...靜丸到底是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 到底是誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎團就讓它充滿謎霧 才顯得神秘充滿魅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉也是 靜丸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人也是
